{"ts":"2026-06-06T12:54:16.209Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/2","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-06T12:54:16.209Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","text":"Post-PR review follow-up: addressed bot feedback by hardening vector collection-name sanitization in runtime+settings normalization, refining rerank candidate construction to remove unsafe non-null assertions/redundant corpus rebuilds, and adding deterministic in-stage rerank resorting + defensive cosine dimension handling. Re-ran full gates: node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (100%), pnpm quality:static (pass), pnpm audit --prod (no vulnerabilities), pnpm changelog:pm:check (pass)."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-06T12:54:16.209Z"}],"before_hash":"bd23f6894a092150b8350adb8ffeb8016b2f252053d05b92b4308424fe0974fc","after_hash":"2bc153b5522b5733132151e41d03334ec3ef821cbfdc63bd04175bc1e9bc9d93"}
{"ts":"2026-06-06T13:03:25.535Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/3","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-06T13:03:25.535Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","text":"Follow-up hardening after review-loop verification: ensured hybrid result ordering keeps reranked candidates ahead of non-reranked candidates when rerank.top_k is smaller than merged hit count. Added regression coverage in tests/unit/search-command.spec.ts (keeps reranked candidates ahead of non-reranked candidates). Re-verified with node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/search-command.spec.ts tests/integration/search-relevance.spec.ts tests/unit/settings-store.spec.ts tests/unit/vector-store-adapter.spec.ts and full gates node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage && pnpm quality:static && pnpm audit --prod && pnpm changelog:pm:check (all passing, coverage still 100%)."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-06T13:03:25.535Z"}],"before_hash":"2bc153b5522b5733132151e41d03334ec3ef821cbfdc63bd04175bc1e9bc9d93","after_hash":"7d4382079a1b0c46545f9856ca6d85fb9b50f5b24bbf1d270a912e70c666b03b"}
{"ts":"2026-06-06T13:13:24.513Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/4","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-06T13:13:24.513Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","text":"Second follow-up after latest bot review: hardened cosine similarity in rerank scoring to short-circuit when dot-product or norm intermediate values are non-finite, preventing invalid score propagation if numeric overflow occurs in rerank embeddings. Added integration regression coverage in tests/integration/search-relevance.spec.ts (handles non-finite cosine intermediates by returning neutral normalized rerank scores). Verification rerun: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/search-relevance.spec.ts tests/unit/search-command.spec.ts and full gates node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage && pnpm quality:static && pnpm audit --prod && pnpm changelog:pm:check; all pass with coverage still 100%."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-06T13:13:24.513Z"}],"before_hash":"7d4382079a1b0c46545f9856ca6d85fb9b50f5b24bbf1d270a912e70c666b03b","after_hash":"d5c7412abba653f6052539cd8c98525c56a79a7f6b28e2ad1daebd5cfc3a1ef7"}
{"ts":"2026-06-06T13:21:10.010Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/5","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-06T13:21:10.010Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","text":"Third follow-up after latest bot review: optimized semantic/hybrid expanded-query execution by running vector lookups concurrently with Promise.all instead of sequential awaits in computeSemanticOrHybridHits. Behavior and ordering remain deterministic because result merging/sorting is unchanged; this reduces latency when query expansion yields multiple variants. Re-verified with node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/search-command.spec.ts tests/integration/search-relevance.spec.ts and full gates node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage && pnpm quality:static && pnpm audit --prod && pnpm changelog:pm:check (all passing, 100% coverage retained)."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-06T13:21:10.010Z"}],"before_hash":"d5c7412abba653f6052539cd8c98525c56a79a7f6b28e2ad1daebd5cfc3a1ef7","after_hash":"b366c8e73e1d004625347f5f25717ebfed16ac90cbfe24546d793f9421da7da4"}
{"ts":"2026-06-06T13:36:21.717Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/6","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-06T13:36:21.717Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","text":"Fourth follow-up after latest bot review: clamped cosine similarity outputs to the mathematically valid [-1,1] range before rerank normalization to guard precision anomalies while retaining existing non-finite intermediate protection. Re-verified with node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/search-relevance.spec.ts tests/unit/search-command.spec.ts plus full gates node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage && pnpm quality:static && pnpm audit --prod && pnpm changelog:pm:check (all passing, coverage unchanged at 100%)."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-06T13:36:21.717Z"}],"before_hash":"b366c8e73e1d004625347f5f25717ebfed16ac90cbfe24546d793f9421da7da4","after_hash":"d5d25844eb1daa12022c721b3a79c0b8a739dcf7f4843ce404d2ec55f1a55539"}
{"ts":"2026-06-06T13:50:18.861Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/7","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-06T13:50:18.861Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","text":"Fifth follow-up after latest bot review: added defensive hardening for relevance/provider edges by (1) lowercasing simple singular/plural normalization inputs, (2) capping resolved rerank top_k at 200, (3) precomputing query L2 norm for rerank cosine scoring to avoid repeated per-candidate norm work, and (4) truncating sanitized vector collection names to 128 chars in both settings normalization and runtime store resolution. Added/updated regression coverage in tests/integration/search-relevance.spec.ts, tests/unit/settings-store.spec.ts, and tests/unit/vector-store-adapter.spec.ts. Full verification rerun passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage, pnpm quality:static, pnpm audit --prod, pnpm changelog:pm:check (all green at 100% coverage)."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-06T13:50:18.861Z"}],"before_hash":"d5d25844eb1daa12022c721b3a79c0b8a739dcf7f4843ce404d2ec55f1a55539","after_hash":"441b219d79b0566f8f93ddb72a1e16ef07875af1e97d16fbe68a09fc4fe042bd"}
